      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Throttle body cleaning"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not place fingers inside the throttle body when the ignition is turned to the ON mode or while the ignition is in the ON mode. If the throttle valve should actuate, it could pinch your fingers and cause serious injury."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Air cleaner element Inspection"
    },
